commits.author: Andrew C. Oliver
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Start a new element without a qname or attributes. * *

This method will provide a default empty attribute * list and an empty string for the qualified name. * It invokes {@link * #startElement(String, String, String, Attributes)} * directly.

* * @param uri The element's Namespace URI. * @param localName The element's local name. * @exception org.xml.sax.SAXException If a filter * further down the chain raises an exception. * @see org.xml.sax.ContentHandler#startElement */ public void startElement (String uri, String localName) throws SAXException { startElement(uri, localName, "", EMPTY_ATTS); }
